    "text": "Updates\nOur Programs\nGet Involved\nMore\nEVENTS\nVOLUNTEER\nDONATE\nKEEP IN TOUCH\nNEWSLETTER\nDONATE\nOur Mission\nSeabury Resources for Aging® provides personalized, affordable services and housing options to help older adults in the greater Washington, D.C. area live with independence and dignity.\nResources & Updates\nProtect Yourself Against Tax-Related Identity Theft\nGet Connected | Internet and Technology Remote Resource Fair\nFalls Prevention Tips\nDonate on GivingTuesday\nPodcast Worth Sharing\nTraining for Faith Leaders\nGIVE ONLINE\nSeabury Resources for Aging® is a 501 (C)(3) nonprofit organization dedicated to providing personalized, affordable services and housing options for older adults in the greater Washington, DC area.\nRead More >>\nBECOME A VOLUNTEER\nHelp build a community where older adults can age with dignity and respect.\nRead More >>\nCONTACT US\nGet in touch with Seabury. \nContact Us >>\nOUR MAJOR PARTNERS\nPlease send all mail to:\nSeabury Resources for Aging®\nP.O. Box 70220\nWashington, DC 20024\nAnnual Reports\nPolicies\nAbout Us\nCareers\nContact Us\nSeabury Resources for Aging® | 555 Water St. SW Washington, DC 20024 | 202-289-5690 | info@seaburyresources.org\nSeabury Resources for Aging® is a private nonprofit 501(c) 3 organization. Seabury’s Identification Number (EIN) is 53-0204693.",
